49:19.680 --> 49:21.700
And I've met, you know, two of his colleagues.

49:21.720 --> 49:22.800
But you're a psyop, dude.

49:22.940 --> 49:24.300
But I'm a psyop, that's right.

49:24.320 --> 49:24.680
They don't, they don't.

49:25.120 --> 49:26.460
Yeah, that's right, that's right.

49:26.500 --> 49:27.040
I'm a psyop.

49:27.400 --> 49:28.320
I don't believe you.

49:28.420 --> 49:30.180
Yeah, well, there you go, there you go.

49:30.540 --> 49:37.120
But it's like, you know, and his friends are like, you hear their frustration, and you see their DD-214, like, their background.

49:37.240 --> 49:38.540
You're like, is anybody seeing this?

49:38.540 --> 49:46.220
And then you have these people, I think it's fine, and I think he would even say it's fine, to go after the experience, be like, I don't know, maybe that was bullshit.

49:46.320 --> 49:47.440
Maybe he was psyoped.

49:48.020 --> 49:52.760
But when they, then they go after his, like, background as, like, a war hero, it's like, come on.

49:52.880 --> 49:53.740
It's a lot, man.

49:53.780 --> 49:54.380
It's a lot.

49:54.380 --> 49:57.060
And it's, no one wants to deal with that.

49:57.200 --> 50:02.160
No, and anyone, all these whistleblowers are watching how everyone's reacting to this stuff.

50:02.340 --> 50:03.560
They're doing their research.

50:03.700 --> 50:08.040
Why would anyone want to be, put themselves out there like that just to get picked apart?

50:08.040 --> 50:08.440
Yeah.

50:08.440 --> 50:10.680
