50:13.000 --> 50:13.880
That's not fun.

50:14.000 --> 50:14.700
It's not fun.

50:14.880 --> 50:17.660
But I'm optimistic after this Wall Street Journal article.

50:18.020 --> 50:20.860
The reason being, I think it's really interesting.

50:20.980 --> 50:25.940
They say it's all part of this Air Force hazing ritual, which is really dumb for the Wall Street Journal to say.

50:26.300 --> 50:34.440
