50:53.240 --> 50:54.600
That does not explain the whole thing.

50:55.040 --> 50:57.740
So they kind of back themselves into this interesting corner.

50:57.740 --> 51:00.780
I think that's the problem is trying to blanket all of it ever.

51:01.160 --> 51:05.300
You know, it's like, I think so many of these things can be true, personally.

51:05.660 --> 51:08.220
I think there's so many parts of it that can be true.

51:09.520 --> 51:11.980
There could be future human.

51:12.140 --> 51:13.440
There could be some grays.

51:13.800 --> 51:16.040
There could be some stuff that we're doing.

51:16.160 --> 51:17.800
It could be some stuff that China's doing.

51:18.040 --> 51:19.920
All these things can exist, I think.

51:20.000 --> 51:20.220
Yeah.

51:20.220 --> 51:21.360
And it probably is.

51:21.420 --> 51:21.740
Yeah.

51:21.740 --> 51:21.920
Yeah.

51:21.920 --> 51:30.060
I've been trying to figure out, personally, well, how I feel about all this stuff, still.

51:30.260 --> 51:36.280
Because I go through this ebb and flow of just kind of being like, I'm always going to be fascinated.

51:36.480 --> 51:36.700
Yeah.

51:36.860 --> 51:41.700
