01:06:18.580 --> 01:06:19.660
How many units are they moving?

01:06:19.660 --> 01:06:19.760
Yeah, right.

01:06:19.760 --> 01:06:29.900
Like, it's like old barbershop conversation or something that has just now become like a very, very popular bit of a conversation, unfortunately.

01:06:30.320 --> 01:06:33.440
