01:06:38.060 --> 01:06:38.320
Yeah.

01:06:38.400 --> 01:06:41.140
I was independently fans of and doing research for this.

01:06:41.140 --> 01:06:41.420
Oh, I like that.

01:06:41.440 --> 01:06:42.460
I was like, I like, like who?

01:06:42.460 --> 01:06:43.860
