01:06:58.440 --> 01:06:59.000
And Daedalus.

01:06:59.000 --> 01:06:59.640
Daedalus.

01:06:59.680 --> 01:07:00.040
Yeah.

01:07:00.420 --> 01:07:02.180
And I'm trying to think.

01:07:02.240 --> 01:07:06.300
