01:07:06.480 --> 01:07:06.780
Yeah.

01:07:06.940 --> 01:07:07.220
Yeah.

01:07:07.400 --> 01:07:09.440
Brain Feeder has been going for a minute, man.

01:07:09.480 --> 01:07:10.380
It's been going for a minute.

01:07:10.380 --> 01:07:26.660
And it's, it's something that I'm actually really, really proud of because it's, it's, you know, something that is kind of flourishing on a, on its own at this point, you know, and I'm still doing a lot of work with Brain Feeder and curating and, you know, the A&R side.

01:07:26.660 --> 01:07:32.580
But, you know, that, that's like a, it's a machine that's moving and it's awesome to see.

01:07:33.020 --> 01:07:39.080
