01:07:39.180 --> 01:07:40.140
Like, I love it.

01:07:40.140 --> 01:07:41.580
You know, it puts you on.

01:07:41.820 --> 01:07:42.020
Absolutely.

01:07:42.460 --> 01:07:52.500
