01:07:57.440 --> 01:07:59.660
You know, I'm not trying to make money there.

01:07:59.860 --> 01:08:02.780
I'm not, it's really not my source of income like that.

01:08:02.780 --> 01:08:05.620
It is, but it's not, you know, at the same time.

01:08:05.800 --> 01:08:09.160
So I just was like, it's, it's my, a passion project.

01:08:09.400 --> 01:08:19.640
But like, I've been so grateful to be able to see all these different artists flourish and have their careers and, you know, they're doing their thing.

01:08:19.880 --> 01:08:20.180
Yeah.

01:08:20.340 --> 01:08:20.940
Being there.

01:08:21.180 --> 01:08:21.340
Yeah.

01:08:21.480 --> 01:08:22.080
Super cool.

