01:11:09.400 --> 01:11:09.600
Yeah.

01:11:09.860 --> 01:11:14.800
I was, I was randomly at dinner and they're, they're playing his music just randomly, you know, and it just comes along.

01:11:14.920 --> 01:11:17.120
